{"tid":2514831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都係焦慮型依戀?","createTime":"2021-05-03T13:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T16:34:29.000Z","uid":61485,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5fc360837d5b0c0fd659b416ae15b3d0a4a768","tid":2514831,"uid":61485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"焦慮型的人懷有很強烈的「想被愛」、「想被接受」、「想被認同」的心情。若問人際關係中最重要的是什麼，他們經常會強調愛與體貼的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n因此，這類型的人對於「被拒絕」、「被拋棄」等事情極度敏感。只要對方露出一點拒絕或否定的舉止，就會感到強烈焦慮，容易對此採取不必要的反應。腦中一旦出現「可能被拒絕」的念頭，就再也難以抹消這種不安的情緒。因此，有時甚至會不斷向對方確認、看著對方臉色、配合對方行動。<br />\n<br />\n以結論來說，焦慮型的人經常無法拒絕或違抗他人。即使面對明顯不當的要求，或是明知自己只是受人利用，他們仍然很難拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n來源:<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/52219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F52219&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=0f49ced3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/52219</a><br />\n<br />\nlocal d黎講即係好chur既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日會想痴住對方會想知道佢到底有幾愛自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf26c094bd6a0813a9eac1528bda1a322a52fd0","tid":2514831,"uid":234307,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"煩撚過閪"},{"pid":"4a929fc15e240ae3b43f5d97776e7d45d4ee1aff","tid":2514831,"uid":61485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbf26c094bd6a0813a9eac1528bda1a322a52fd0","tid":2514831,"uid":234307,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"煩撚過閪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58a002afde2168776f9dc49c081afce5cbd9547","tid":2514831,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"做乜呢排咁多呢d咩春依戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff8bf404a2